content: Very very accurate recreation! One minor point, not a criticism: you get far more bonus saucers than in the original. A major plus point is an extra life every 1500 points, instead of just the first 1500!
Excellent. I had this for my Windows phone but this version is even better with more options. Great nostalgic fun and runs so smooth. Time to chase my high score...
The most faithful and authentic rendition of the original I've seen, exactly what I was craving. Silky smooth frame rate to boot!
